title: Avail September - 1 Bed + Den/Office
posting_body: ['Contact Information', 'Olympus Properties', '612 886-RENT(7368)', 'Avail September - 1 Bed + Second Room for Office, Den, or Small Bedroom - in Historical Building with New Updates - Walking Distance from Downtown / Great Neighborhood - $979 per month', '214 East 19th Street', 'FEATURES', 'Bedrooms:', '1', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Located on Floor #:', '3', 'Pets Allowed:', 'Cats and Dogs, Fees Apply', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Walking distance to downtown!', 'Close to Stevens Square Park and featuring in-building the neighborhood favorite Boiler Room Coffee shop.', 'The Darthmouth and The Castleton offer large units, ample light, designer paint colors, updated wooden blinds, built-in cabinets, new appliances, and other new upgrades.', 'Olympus Properties, LLC | (612) 886-RENT (7368)', 'Equal Opportunity Housing', 'BUILDING AMENITIES', 'On-site Laundry', 'Secured Access', 'Non-smoking Building', 'Boiler Room Coffee on-site', 'Parking Available for Rent', 'LINKS', 'Olympus Properties, LLC -', '<URL>', 'OTHER PRICING DETAILS:', 'Available Date: September', 'Deposit:  $500.00', 'Included Utilities:   Heat, Hot and Cold Water, Trash/Recycling, Sewage']
